Interface PatientMenu

All Superinterfaces:
CommonMenu
All Known Implementing Classes:
PatientUI
public interface PatientMenu extends CommonMenu
This interface extends CommonMenu to provide functionalities specific to managing a patient's personal information. It defines a method for updating a patient's personal details within the system.

The methods in this interface are intended to be implemented by classes that provide the actual functionality for handling the patient's personal information update.
